room_title: Escape room "Wizard's Keep" by Mind Games Clovis in Fresno
room_address: 30 W Shaw Ave, Suite 108 Clovis, CA 93612
room_description: Tragedy has befallen the Kingdom! His Majesty lies ill, his royal Wizard struck down. Other than the Wizard, you (as his apprentices) were the only ones who had access to the rare and deadly poison. Don’t tarry in your search for the antidote, the King’s guard are on their way to take you to the dungeon. Can you find it in time to save your King and Kingdom… and yourselves?
